The green fluorescence was seen in the cytoplasm of the COS-7 cells transfected with pTriEx3-4F/4R with transfusion reagent or DPH complex without transfusion reagent, indicating the expression of TCoV 4F/4R S fragment in COS-7 cells (Fig. 1
). Purified TCoV 4F/4R S fragment was detected by the serum collected from TCoV-infected turkey on Western blotting with a size of 26 kDa (Fig. 2
).
